*******************************************************************

Name:    at (Do a command at a player without moving)

Desc:    This command allows you to do an action in environment of 
         player as though you were there
    

Level:   50   

Warning: 

Syntax:  at <player> <cmd>

Example: at fred punt fred 
Result:  You punt Fred 43 yards. Damn, you booted Fred's ass!

Related: 

*******************************************************************